{"type": "article", "id": 13766, "title": "防水 Apple Watch 保护壳", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-20T07:45:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000302o7VuWf9OQ6qRrUnj.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tCatalyst 最近推出了一款防水 Apple Watch 保护壳，采用混合塑胶的橡胶材质，可以保证手表在1米的水深处仍然可以保证良好的防水性能，同时，产品搭配了一个可以快速拆卸和安装的24毫米 NATO 尼龙表带。三种款式分别名为 “Stealth Black”，“Rescue Ranger”，“Green Pop” ，这是<a href=\"http://www.catalystlifestyle.com/collections/frontpage/products/preorder-catalyst-apple-watch-42mm\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141446MonELSOH1Fy3bpI5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141447BQCzG8V90AnrFswd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141447soE6egcfyJFQZv1b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141448PZl7X2Uxi95LmE4z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141449CSPq9Qg1nf3UvB0c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141449WaMwhkl2UJZviQe8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141450r34RfzSqPGLYeN0h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}